  "text": "Identified 13 core source files spanning Raft consensus integration, lease management, and liveness-based health checking. The Raft ready pipeline flows: raftScheduler (scheduler.go) enqueues work -> Store.processReady (store_raft.go) dispatches to replicas -> Replica.handleRaftReady/handleRaftReadyRaftMuLocked (replica_raft.go) processes the raft Ready struct -> replicaStateMachine.ApplySideEffects (replica_application_state_machine.go) applies committed entries. Lease management centers on replica_range_lease.go (requestLeaseLocked, AdminTransferLease, redirectOnOrAcquireLease), with batch evaluation in batcheval/cmd_lease_request.go (RequestLease) and batcheval/cmd_lease_transfer.go (TransferLease). Lease type selection (expiration vs epoch-based) and construction lives in leases/build.go (leaseType, leaseExpiration, leaseEpoch, build functions), with lease status evaluation in leases/status.go (Status function) and kvserverpb/lease_status.go (LeaseStatus type). Node health checking feeds into lease decisions via liveness/liveness.go (NodeLiveness type, ScanNodeVitalityFromKV, GetIsLiveMap, GetNodeVitalityFromCache), liveness/livenesspb/liveness.go (Liveness.IsLive, NodeVitality.IsLive, LivenessStatus), and liveness/cache.go (Cache with ScanNodeVitalityFromCache, GetNodeVitality).",
